    "Title": "[AI 摘要] 台股創高46459點！台積電續創新天價2425元",
    "Content": "台股今日再度暴衝，盤中最高上漲近千點，創下歷史新高46552點，收盤仍上漲901點，漲幅1.98％，收在46459點，同樣是收盤新高  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E9%A4%90%E9%A3%B2%E6%A5%AD%E4%B9%9F%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB-%E6%BC%A2%E4%BE%86%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%8970%E5%BC%B5-125555884.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a>。台積電早盤大漲55元，報2435元達到新天價，午盤漲幅雖微幅縮減，終場上漲45元收2425元  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E9%80%993%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%BA%BA%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-%E9%9F%93%E5%AA%92%E7%8B%82%E8%AE%9A%E9%BB%83%E4%BB%81%E5%8B%B3-%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%8E%E9%AB%94%E6%8B%BF%E7%A0%B4%E5%B4%99-%E7%B7%A0%E9%80%A0%E7%A5%9E%E8%A9%B1-075638939.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[2]</a>。\n\n台北國際電腦展（COMPUTEX）帶動AI題材熱度，推升台股再創新高  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BB%96%E5%95%8F-600%E8%90%AC%E6%80%8E%E7%BF%BB%E6%88%902%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E9%87%A3%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%9E-%E7%9E%AC%E9%96%93%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%86-050300602.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[3]</a>。三大法人同步站在買方，合計買超515.65億元，其中外資買超433.96億元，呈現連4買  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BB%96%E5%95%8F-600%E8%90%AC%E6%80%8E%E7%BF%BB%E6%88%902%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E9%87%A3%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%9E-%E7%9E%AC%E9%96%93%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%86-050300602.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[3]</a>。\n\n重點分析\n資料來源：Yahoo奇摩股市、鉅亨網、經濟日報 | 期間：過去 48 小時\n\n台股今日延續多頭氣勢，盤中及收盤指數均創歷史新高，終場上漲901.85點，收在46459.16點，成交金額達1兆4508.77億元  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E7%9A%87%E7%BF%945-25-6-1%E8%99%95%E5%88%86%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB220%E5%BC%B5-%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%A9%E7%B4%842822%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-004600269.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[4]</a>。權值股王台積電收盤價2425元創歷史新高，漲幅1.89%  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BBadr%E9%80%B1-%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%884-11-%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E5%A4%A9%E5%83%B9-%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E5%8A%8D%E6%8C%87%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E4%BA%94%E5%93%A5%E4%BA%9E%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%9C-001659160.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[5]</a>。聯發科、鴻海、台達電等權值股亦有不錯表現，但台光電下跌  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BBadr%E9%80%B1-%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%884-11-%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E5%A4%A9%E5%83%B9-%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E5%8A%8D%E6%8C%87%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E4%BA%94%E5%93%A5%E4%BA%9E%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%9C-001659160.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[5]</a>。記憶體族群則表現疲軟，南亞科及華邦電均下跌超過3%  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%BC%9D%E9%81%94%E7%AB%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC-%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E7%99%BE%E5%84%84%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%8A-%E9%80%99%E5%8F%B0%E5%BB%A0-%E6%82%84%E6%82%84%E8%B2%B7%E6%88%90%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%8C%81%E8%82%A1-010700820.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[6]</a>。COMPUTEX展登場帶動AI概念股持續熱絡，盤中最高達46552.16點  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BB%96%E5%95%8F-600%E8%90%AC%E6%80%8E%E7%BF%BB%E6%88%902%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E9%87%A3%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%9E-%E7%9E%AC%E9%96%93%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%86-050300602.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[3]</a>。高盛報告看好北亞市場，將台灣加權指數評級上調至「增持」，目標價調升至5.1萬點  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%97%A9%E7%9B%A4-%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E6%BC%B2%E8%B7%8C%E4%BA%92%E7%8F%BE-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E8%A7%80%E6%9C%9B%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E8%88%87ai%E9%A1%8C%E6%9D%90-134228961.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[7]</a>。"
  },
  {
    "Ticker": "2454.TW",
