8-5%E5%A4%A7%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E-%E6%AC%A1%E7%9C%8B-%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E9%A9%9A%E5%96%8A%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%83%B93%E5%AD%97%E9%A0%AD-003631624.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a>。台積電的強勢表現帶動台股早盤漲861.37點，達46418.68點，台股同步創新高  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/1%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E8%AE%80%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E8%82%A1%E6%9D%B1%E6%9C%83%E5%80%92%E6%95%B8-5%E5%A4%A7%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E-%E6%AC%A1%E7%9C%8B-%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E9%A9%9A%E5%96%8A%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%83%B93%E5%AD%97%E9%A0%AD-003631624.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a>。台達電上揚95元至2455元，鴻海漲4.5元至306元，顯示權值股普遍走強  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/1%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E8%AE%80%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E8%82%A1%E6%9D%B1%E6%9C%83%E5%80%92%E6%95%B8-5%E5%A4%A7%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E-%E6%AC%A1%E7%9C%8B-%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E9%A9%9A%E5%96%8A%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%83%B93%E5%AD%97%E9%A0%AD-003631624.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a>。Computex展覽期間AI利多消息不斷，相關供應鏈成為市場焦點，資金湧向記憶體及AI概念股  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E8%82%A1%E6%9D%B1%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%AC%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B4-%E5%A0%B1%E5%83%B9%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E7%AD%89%E8%AD%B0%E9%A1%8C%E6%96%99%E6%88%90%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E-014000891.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[3]</a>。市場對台股後市抱持樂觀態度，認為今年挑戰5萬點大關的機會依然存在  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%B2%A1%E5%A0%B1%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%95%E7%8D%B2%E5%A5%A7%E6%9C%AC%E6%B5%B7%E9%BB%98%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80%E5%89%8D%E7%9E%BB-%E5%8D%9A%E9%80%9A%E4%B8%8A%E9%80%B1%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E6%BC%B24-7-%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E9%80%BC%E8%BF%91%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB-001906192.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[2]</a>。"
