5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BBadr%E9%80%B1-%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%884-11-%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E5%A4%A9%E5%83%B9-%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E5%8A%8D%E6%8C%87%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E4%BA%94%E5%93%A5%E4%BA%9E%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%9C-001659160.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[5]</a>。聯發科、鴻海、台達電等權值股亦有不錯表現，但台光電下跌  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BBadr%E9%80%B1-%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%884-11-%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E5%A4%A9%E5%83%B9-%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E5%8A%8D%E6%8C%87%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E4%BA%94%E5%93%A5%E4%BA%9E%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%9C-001659160.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[5]</a>。記憶體族群則表現疲軟，南亞科及華邦電均下跌超過3%  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%BC%9D%E9%81%94%E7%AB%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC-%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E7%99%BE%E5%84%84%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%8A-%E9%80%99%E5%8F%B0%E5%BB%A0-%E6%82%84%E6%82%84%E8%B2%B7%E6%88%90%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%8C%81%E8%82%A1-010700820.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[6]</a>。COMPUTEX展登場帶動AI概念股持續熱絡，盤中最高達46552.16點  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BB%96%E5%95%8F-600%E8%90%AC%E6%80%8E%E7%BF%BB%E6%88%902%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E9%87%A3%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%9E-%E7%9E%AC%E9%96%93%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%86-050300602.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[3]</a>。高盛報告看好北亞市場，將台灣加權指數評級上調至「增持」，目標價調升至5.1萬點  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%97%A9%E7%9B%A4-%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E6%BC%B2%E8%B7%8C%E4%BA%92%E7%8F%BE-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E8%A7%80%E6%9C%9B%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E8%88%87ai%E9%A1%8C%E6%9D%90-134228961.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[7]</a>。"
